    <summary>Silent, prompt-free Windows cache cleaner — passwords and Downloads never touched.</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
## My Clean PC

One-click Windows cache cleaner with **zero dialogs** and **zero prompts**.

### What it cleans
- Windows Temp folders (`%TEMP%`, `C:\Windows\Temp`)
- LocalAppData and Roaming AppData junk / cache folders
- Browser caches for all detected browsers (Chrome, Edge, Firefox, Brave, Vivaldi, …)
- Windows Disk Cleanup (`C:` drive, downloads categories excluded)
- Recycle Bin, Windows Update download cache, DNS cache, Event Logs

### What it never touches
- Passwords / Login Data
- Autofill and form data
- Bookmarks
- Downloads folder
- Quick Access pins

### How it avoids dialogs
Uses `del /f /s /q` + Robocopy `/MIR` for all directory wipes.  
Locked files are silently skipped; any remaining locks are registered for silent deletion at next reboot.  
The Explorer "Do this for all items" prompt is **never** shown.

### Space-freed counter
Displays how many GB/MB were reclaimed at the end of every run.
    ]]></description>
